# 🧠 OS Concept 1: Rate Limiting

🔥 Very important API/backend topic.

---

## 1️⃣ Simple Idea

Limit how many requests a user/system can send in given time.

---

## Example

```text id="7m2qpk"
100 requests/minute
```

If exceeded:

❌ requests blocked or delayed.

---

## Why Needed?

✔ prevent abuse
✔ avoid overload
✔ improve stability
✔ protect APIs

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Water tap allowing limited flow.

---

## Common Techniques

* Token bucket
* Leaky bucket

(Only basics needed for placements.)

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why rate limiting important?**

👉 Because it prevents overload and protects services from excessive traffic.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="4x8mtr"
Too many requests → slow/block them
```

