# ⚙️ COA Concept 4: AI Accelerator Interconnects

🔥 Modern AI infrastructure topic.

---

## 1️⃣ Problem

Large AI training uses many GPUs/TPUs.

They must communicate quickly.

---

## Interconnects

Special high-speed communication links.

Examples:

* NVLink
* InfiniBand

---

## Why Important?

Slow communication causes:

❌ training bottlenecks
❌ synchronization delays

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Fast highways between factories.

---

## 🔗 Connection

Critical for:

* distributed AI training
* model parallelism

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

**Q: Why fast interconnects important in AI systems?**

👉 Because GPUs exchange huge amounts of training data and parameters.

---

## 🧠 Memory Trick

```text id="3r8mqt"
Many GPUs need fast communication
```

